videos.description: Clemson's Ray-Ray McCloud makes the catch but loses the ball inside his own 20 and Auburn recovers the fumble.
videos.headline: Auburn forces fumble deep in Clemson territory

videos.description: Kelly Bryant completes the pass but gets hit very hard and is forced to leave the game in the second quarter.
videos.headline: Clemson's Bryant takes big hit and has to leave the game

videos.description: Deon Cain jumps high in the sky and makes the great grab for a 20-yard gain.
videos.headline: Clemson's Cain rises up and makes the jumping catch

videos.description: Kelly Bryant runs right up the middle for a touchdown to put Clemson on top.
videos.headline: Bryant's TD gives Clemson lead late in the 1st half

videos.description: Ray-Ray McCloud makes the nice catch for a 29-yard gain and puts Clemson  into the red zone.
videos.headline: Clemson's McCloud makes the nice over-the-shoulder catch

videos.description: Clemson head coach Dabo Swinney is pleased with the way QB Kelly Bryant handled the adversity and hopes the offense gets into a rhythm in the second half.
videos.headline: Dabo Swinney happy to lead despite offensive struggle

videos.description: Kelly Bryant exits the game in the second quarter after a big hit but returns and runs up the middle to put Clemson up 7-6 at the half.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Clemson takes slim lead into half) 2017/9/9 ESHEET ENHL

videos.headline: Clemson takes slim lead into half

videos.description: Kelly Bryant floats the perfect pass to Ray-Ray McCloud for a big pickup.
videos.headline: McCloud makes another nice grab for 33-yard gain

videos.description: Kelly Bryant uses his strength to get past the defenders and score the 27-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Bryant breaks a tackle and gets his 2nd rushing TD

videos.description: Clelin Ferrell gets around the line, puts the big hit on the Jarrett Stidham to force the fumble but Auburn would recover.
videos.headline: Clemson's Ferrell with the big hit on the QB and forces the fumble

videos.description: Marlon Davidson puts the hit on Clemson's C.J. Fuller and forces another turnover for the Tigers.
videos.headline: Auburn's defense forces another fumble

videos.description: Tre Lamar with the great pass rush to sack Jarrett Stidham and Clemson takes over.
videos.headline: Clemson's defense gets big sack on 4th down

videos.description: Eight sacks is the most the Tigers  have had in one game since 2004, when they recorded 11.
videos.headline: Clemson's defense picks up their 8th sack of the game

videos.description: Austin Bryant is the latest Tiger to sack Jarrett Stidham and Clemson is one sack shy of the school record.
videos.headline: Clemson's defense picks up their 11th sack of the game

videos.description: Clemson coach Dabo Swinney praises his team's effort in a big out-of-conference win and how his quarterback Kelly Bryant handled adversity.
videos.headline: Swinney happy with the way his defense played tonight

videos.description: Kelly Bryant shines for Clemson with his feet, running for two touchdowns in the 14-6 win over Auburn.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Bryant fuels Clemson past Auburn) 2017/9/9 ESHEET ENHL

videos.headline: Bryant fuels Clemson past Auburn

videos.description: QB Kelly Bryant runs for two touchdowns and DE Austin Bryant records four of the Tigers' 11 sacks to lead Clemson past Auburn 14-6.
videos.headline: The Bryants lead the way for Clemson

videos.description: Clemson WR Hunter Renfrow says that he and his teammates have seen Bryant's leadership all throughout camp and he showed the world today what he's capable of.
